<dl id="n03024g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03024g">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03024g"> 24(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ servant</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> <font color="green">[Story of Riquier, a nobleman and later a saint, and missionaries whom he protected.]</font> He learned from them to love God above all things, and was filled with sorrow for his past life which he had spent as an <mark>unfruitful servant</mark>. <small> J.M. Flood, <a name="JMFI" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JMFI"><cite title="source">Ireland: Its Saints and Scholars</cite></a> (n.d) 62</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
